flowchart LR
  S[Scheme definition] --> A[Application]
  A --> P[Assessment plan]
  P --> E[Evidence collection and testing]
  E --> F[Findings]
  F --> D[Independent decision]
  D --> C[Certificate or claim]
  C --> R[Public status]
  R --> V[Surveillance]
  V -->|maintained| R
  V -->|nonconformity| N[Remediation or restriction]
  N -->|resolved| R
  N -->|unresolved| W[Suspension or withdrawal]
